org.jredis.ri.alphazero
Class VirtualResponse

java.lang.Object
  org.jredis.ri.alphazero.VirtualResponse
All Implemented Interfaces:
Message, Response
public final class VirtualResponse
extends java.lang.Object
implements Response

Certain requested commands do not have a corresponding response from redis. Quit and Shutdown are two examples as of now. This response provides a virtual response for this type of request. You can set the virtual response's status in the constructor. The default constructor provides for OK status.

alpha.0
